og.description: Nurse practitioners are seeing annual net incomes surpass $100,000 as their roles expand amid a doctor shortage, changing state regulations and the push toward team-based approaches to keeping patients healthy and costs in check. A new report by the American Association of Nurse Practitioners shows total annual income increasing this year [...]
